{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LmvPiU5UhwcqmaitUt4erb","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package ports\n     2→\n     3→import (\n     4→\t\"context\"\n     5→\t\"io\"\n     6→\t\"time\"\n     7→)\n     8→\n     9→type ContainerStatus struct {\n    10→\tRunning    bool\n    11→\tExitCode   int\n    12→\tFinishedAt time.Time\n    13→}\n    14→\n    15→type ContainerConfig struct {\n    16→\tImage        string\n    17→\tWorkflowName string\n    18→\tProjectDir   string\n    19→\tNetworkAllow []string\n    20→\tRunID        string\n    21→\tCmd          []string // override container command; defaults to [\"cloche-agent\", WorkflowName]\n    22→}\n    23→\n    24→type ContainerRuntime interface {\n    25→\tStart(ctx context.Context, cfg ContainerConfig) (containerID string, err error)\n    26→\tStop(ctx context.Context, containerID string) error\n    27→\tAttachOutput(ctx context.Context, containerID string) (io.ReadCloser, error)\n    28→\tWait(ctx context.Context, containerID string) (exitCode int, err error)\n    29→\tCopyFrom(ctx context.Context, containerID string, srcPath, dstPath string) error\n    30→\tLogs(ctx context.Context, containerID string) (string, error)\n    31→\tRemove(ctx context.Context, containerID string) error\n    32→\tInspect(ctx context.Context, containerID string) (*ContainerStatus, error)\n    33→}\n    34→\n    35→// ImageEnsurer is an optional interface that a ContainerRuntime may implement\n    36→// to validate and rebuild container images when the project Dockerfile has\n    37→// changed since the last build.\n    38→type ImageEnsurer interface {\n    39→\tEnsureImage(ctx context.Context, projectDir, image string) error\n    40→}\n    41→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01KxSmpApK5xnCTuSmWZ7Zh8","session_id":"b2566a3c-e8d8-43a6-bf93-08a9f5a6e841","uuid":"b8fcc42f-56e6-4b29-bb03-571a3b689cd8"}
